{"timestamp": "2025-12-06 12:38:21.561088", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submitted the diagnosis:\n\n- Anomaly: true\n- Faulty devices: leaf_1, leaf_2, spine_1\n- Root cause(s): flow_rule_loop, p4_table_entry_missing\n\nRationale:\n- Hairpin flows on leaf_1 and leaf_2 (in_port -> same port) create a loopback/blackhole behavior for access hosts, consistent with a flow rule loop misprogramming.\n- Missing broadcast/ARP/unknown-unicast handling and absence of unicast entries for all but one host pair indicates missing table entries installed by the controller.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2016, "output_tokens": 120, "total_tokens": 2136, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1920}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
